────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
  Keybindings

    Global
      Ctrl+C       Cancel current turn / interrupt
      Ctrl+D       Exit AGI Workforce
      Ctrl+L       Clear screen (preserve session)
      Tab          Toggle plan mode
      Shift+Tab    Cycle plan / accept / reject

    Slash palette
      /            Open palette
      ↑/↓          Navigate commands
      Enter        Run selected command
      Esc          Close palette
      type         Filter commands

    Overlays
      ←/→          Switch tabs
      ↑/↓          Navigate items
      Enter        Confirm / open detail
      Esc          Close overlay

    Editor
      Ctrl+E       Open external editor for current input
      Alt+Enter    Insert newline without submitting

  Esc to close
